---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="page">
    <div class="grid hero-top">
      <div class="section-num-col">
        <span class="section-num">/01 — Intro</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-head">
        <h1>
          Código<br>
          <span class="thin">que</span> <span class="red-bar">resuelve</span><br>
          problemas.
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="divider hero-divider"></div>

    <div class="grid hero-bottom">
      <div class="section-num-col">
        <span class="section-num">Sobre</span>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-desc-col">
        <p class="lead">
          <strong>Juan Unanue.</strong> Desarrollador independiente, estudio propio.<br>
          Construyo sitios web y sistemas de gestión a medida —sin plantillas, sin atajos— para negocios que quieren operar mejor y crecer en serio.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-cta">
          <a href="/#proyectos" class="btn">→ Ver trabajo</a>
          <a href="/#contacto" class="btn btn-secondary">→ Escribir</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-info-col">
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="label">Status</span>
          <span class="value">● Disponible</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="label">Clientes</span>
          <span class="value">02 Activos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="label">Base</span>
          <span class="value">Argentina</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-item">
          <span class="label">Desde</span>
          <span class="value">2024</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 5rem 0 4rem;
    min-height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-top { margin-bottom: 3rem; }

  .section-num-col {
    grid-column: 1 / 3;
    padding-top: 0.3rem;
  }

  .hero-head {
    grid-column: 3 / 13;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 0.85;
    letter-spacing: -0.045em;
  }

  .hero h1 .thin {
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .hero-divider { margin: 2rem 0; }

  .hero-bottom {
    align-items: start;
  }

  .hero-desc-col {
    grid-column: 3 / 8;
  }

  .hero-info-col {
    grid-column: 9 / 13;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .hero-info-col .info-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  .hero .value {
    color: var(--color-black);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-black);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .lead strong {
    font-weight: 900;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .section-num-col { grid-column: 1 / -1; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero-head,
    .hero-desc-col,
    .hero-info-col { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
    .hero-info-col { margin-top: 2rem; }
  }
</style>
